# Do’s and Don’ts of Prompting

## Do’s

- Be specific
- Give context
- Mention the format you want
- Ask for examples
- Mention the tone if needed
- Refine the prompt if the answer is not good
- Break large tasks into smaller prompts
- Use simple and clear language

## Don’ts

- Do not ask vague questions
- Do not expect perfect answers in one try
- Do not give incomplete instructions
- Do not combine too many tasks in one prompt
- Do not use confusing language
- Do not forget to mention the topic clearly
- Do not blindly trust every AI response
- Do not ask unrelated things in the same prompt
